org.bytedeco.tensorflowlite

Class TfLitePtrUnion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.tensorflowlite.TfLitePtrUnion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @Properties(inherit=tensorflowlite.class)
public class TfLitePtrUnion
extends Pointer
    A union of pointers that points to memory for a given tensor. Do not access these members directly, if possible, use GetTensorData<TYPE>(tensor) instead, otherwise only access .data, as other members are deprecated.
